        <item>
            <title>本田全電動折疊電單車 Motocompacto 0.6 匹馬力＋12 英里續航力售 $7,780</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/24/motocompacto/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=motocompacto</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/24/motocompacto/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 24 Sep 2023 07:01:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Motocompacto]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全電動折疊電單車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[本田]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1194527</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日發布全電動折疊電單車 Motocompacto，其馬力為 0.6 匹，續航力達 12 英里，預計於 11 月正式推出。</p><p>與先前由二衝程循環驅動的 Motocompo 有別，Motocompacto 由電力驅動，續航力達 12 英里，最高時速為 15 英里/小時，最大扭力 15Nm。整輛 Motocompacto 僅重 18.7 公斤，總承載能力為 120 公斤，其折疊式設計它可折成手提行李箱大小，成年用家更可將腿搭在 Motocompacto 上。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1-694x537.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="537" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1-694x537.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1-1163x900.jpg 1163w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1-768x595.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_1.4988b272cec2a07d4a05-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769-694x537.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="537" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769-694x537.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769-1163x900.jpg 1163w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769-768x595.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/moto_fit_5.4d807e36dd6c699a2769.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Motocompo 的馬達裝在前輪，後輪則裝有鼓式煞車，採用 6.8Ah 電池，支援家用插座充電，充電時間僅為 3.5 小時。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_63.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194538" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_63-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_63-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_63-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_63.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_65.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_65-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_65-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_65-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_65.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_66.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_66-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_66-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_66-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/honda-motocompacto_66.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>現時本田表示 Motocompacto 將透過專用的 Motocompacto 網站以及本田和 Acura 經銷商在美國上市，預計於 11 月正式推出，建議零售價為 995 美元（約 HK$7,780）。 外媒推測 Motocompacto 主攻學生市場，為騎單車上學的學生提供既嶄新又經濟實惠的上學方式。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_16542"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XzkSthZHRiI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>圖片來源：本田</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.visordown.com/news/new-bikes/all-electric-honda-motocompacto-announced">Visordown</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
