        </item>
        <item>
            <title>微軟 Surface Laptop Go 3  配備 15 小時續航力、Intel 第 12 代 Core i5 處理器</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/24/microsoft-surface-laptop-go-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-surface-laptop-go-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/24/microsoft-surface-laptop-go-3/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 24 Sep 2023 06:58:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1194759</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 秋季發布會以更新的手提電腦「Surface Laptop Go 3」打響頭炮，該電腦擁有 15 小時續航力，機身僅重約 1.13kg，於 10 月 3 日推出。</p><p>12.4 吋的「Surface Laptop Go 3」機身上蓋採用陽極鋁，底板採用具有玻璃纖維與 30% 再生成分的鋁與聚碳酸脂複合。其外觀和前代相比變化不大，延續系列以輕盈、便利攜帶的基本型產品設計。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.51-694x478.png" alt="" width="694" height="478" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.51-694x478.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.51-1280x882.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.51-768x529.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.51.png 1312w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.40-694x534.png" alt="" width="694" height="534" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.40-694x534.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.40-1169x900.png 1169w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.40-768x591.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.29.40.png 1294w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/d/surface-laptop-go-3/8p0wwgj6c6l2">microsoft</a>）</p><p>不過其採用了 Intel 第 12 代 Core i5 處理器，同時有 Iris Xe 內建顯卡和最高 16GB LPDDR5 RAM 及 512GB 儲存，亦可選擇 8GB 或 16GB LPDDR5 記憶體，與可替換的 256GB SSD。</p><p>Surface Laptop Go 3 配備 3:2 PixelSense 10 點觸控觸控螢幕，外覆康寧 Gorilla 3 玻璃，有 USB 3.2 Type-C 複合插槽，其中包括數據、 DP 與充電，並且有 USB 3.1 Type-A，以及 Surface 連接埠。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1194767 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.18-694x374.png" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.18-694x374.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.18-1280x689.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.18-768x414.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.18.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/d/surface-laptop-go-3/8p0wwgj6c6l2">microsoft</a>）</p><p>而新機電池為 41Wh ，最大續航力可達 15 小時，系統採用 Windows 11 家用版，並支援韌體 TPM 2.0 、整合於新增的電源鍵指紋辨識器。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194769 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.12-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.12-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.12-1280x730.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.12-768x438.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.12.png 1364w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1194768 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.26-694x398.png" alt="" width="694" height="398" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.26-694x398.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.26-1280x734.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.26-768x441.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-12.30.26.png 1370w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/d/surface-laptop-go-3/8p0wwgj6c6l2">microsoft</a>）</p><p>Surface Laptop Go 3 的售價由 799.99 美金起（約港幣＄6,255 元）， 共提供藍、粉、綠、灰四種配色，預計今年 10 月 3 日於特定國家陸續推出。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_96163"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IXJPVQws7_M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/d/surface-laptop-go-3/8p0wwgj6c6l2">microsoft</a>、<a href="https://www.notebookcheck.net/Microsoft-Surface-Laptop-Go-3-arrives-as-minor-refresh-with-performance-and-battery-life-improvements.753848.0.html">notebookcheck</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
